        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto" color="#000000">
          <h2 style="font-size:20px;line-height:1.2;font-weight:500; margin-top:2px;">UN aid halted</h2>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-image padding="10px 12px" width="600px" src="https://www.geopolitics.world/email/images/gp-dec-3-1.jpg" alt="UN aid halted" href="https://www.geopolitics.world" />
        <mj-text padding="10px 12px" font-family="Roboto+Serif" color="#000000">
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.4;">UNRWA has <a href="https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/c1ln5592v46o" target="_blank">suspended</a> aid deliveries through Gaza's <a href="https://www.google.com/maps/place/Kerem+Shalom+check-point/@31.2187718,34.2716332,15z/data=!4m6!3m5!1s0x14fded5a787b5811:0x87f384d8c2a9944f!8m2!3d31.219044!4d34.2724963!16s%2Fg%2F11rc9wn5vh?entry=ttu&g_ep=EgoyMDI0MTEyNC4xIKXMDSoASAFQAw%3D%3D" target="_blank">Kerem Shalom crossing</a> due to escalating theft and insecurity. This announcement is a result of two recent loots by armed gangs near the crossing and the death of three people employed by the <a href="https://wck.org/" target="_blank">World Central Kitchen</a>. On 16 November, a convoy of 107 trucks was attacked by masked men and looted 97 lorries. The locals and aid workers have accused the gang of operating in plain sight of the Israel Defense Forces in a restricted area. UNRWA chief Philippe Lazzarini has called on Israel to restore law and order to ensure the safe passage of humanitarian aid.</p>
          <p style="font-size:16px;line-height:1.4;">Israel accuses Hamas of stealing and profiting from the aid. The Coordinator of Government Activities in the Territories <a href="https://x.com/cogatonline/status/1863250932378501351" target="_blank">mentioned</a> that only 7% of the aid that came to the Gaza Strip was coordinated by UNRWA and there were other humanitarian organizations delivering aid in response to the announcement. The situation continues to deteriorate in Gaza, which is now facing a potential famine as aid shipments are at their lowest levels since the conflict began in October 2023.​</p>
        </mj-text>
        <mj-divider border-width="1px" border-style="solid" border-color="lightgrey" padding="10px 12px" />
      </mj-column>
    </mj-section>
    <!-- Content sections -->
    <mj-section css-class="mj_section" background-color="#ffffff">
